.SH NAME
SDL_GL_SwapWindow \- Update a window with OpenGL rendering\[char46]
.SH HEADER FILE
Defined in SDL3/SDL_video\[char46]h

.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
.B #include \(dqSDL3/SDL.h\(dq
